no     our strategy we are consistently finetuning our strategies and strengthening our innovative core to anticipate and lead change in the global digital landscape win customers for life vision our vision is to enrich the lives of our customers our obsession is to win customers for life through exceptional experience objectives grow market share profitably accelerate nonmobile businesses values alive inclusive respectful how we will win  win through gotomarket excellence grow share of new smartphones and g devices accelerate data penetration via intuitive pricing and innovation build india’s no  payments bank through a “frugal and digital” model  win with a brilliant network experience eliminate customer frustration through quality obsession improve customer advocacy through granular planning and communication drive down unit cost per mb through leveraging multiple technologies  win with valuable customers grow gg data by encouraging consumption bundling and upgradation grow postpaid through propositions store experience and bb drive accelerate bb through improved experience scale homes through highspeed broadband lowcost access and bundling win dth through disproportionate share of digitization and innovation  win with a war on waste drive down cost lower costs and maximise sharing cut waste by network redesign  win with people highperformance culture grow talent through strong learning mentoring and succession planning financial snapshot organization structure bharti airtel limited  organization structure india and south asia md  ceo india and south asia gopal vittal coo india and se asia bharti airtel ajai puri director consumer business raj pudipeddi director customer experience sarang kanade director  ceo airtel business ashok ganapathy director  ceo  global voice  data business ajay chitkara ceo directtohome sunil taldar ceo airtel payments bank shashi arora ceo nxtra neil pollock   cto abhay savargaonkar   global chro b srikanth   global cfo nilanjan roy   